{"about_the_game":"<strong>THE FIRST STEALTH GAME SET IN THE MERCILESS AND FRENETIC WORLD OF WORK! </strong><br><br>Gary is an office worker who overslept after a drunken night out in town. Here's where it gets tricky, because this isn't the first time Gary's been late for work, and he could be fired if he's spotted arriving at his desk after everyone else yet again. So he\u2019ll have to prove his smartness and slyness to make his way up the 22 floors standing between him and his office without being caught.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/431290/extras/Fired600.jpg?t=1720186494\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hide in closets, crawl through air vents, slink along the walls\u2026 nobody must spot you!<br></li><li>Use everything in your reach to get to the end of the level: hide behind a newspaper, smash a vending machine with a well-aimed kick, or use donuts to lure the security guards away.<br></li><li>Want to drive your colleagues crazy, knock them out, poison them or even expose them to harmful radiation?<br></li><li>Fool photocopiers, stroll hiding in a cardboard box or distribute laxatives ... It is possible in Level 22!<br></li><li>Ready to settle the score with your bosses?</li></ul><br>From the basement to the boss\u2019s office via the research and development labs, explore the zany little universe of LEVEL 22.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Dark Bat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/431290/1866b90cdfe19b802ebc108fefb4134e88d20a26.jpg"},{"name":"Clawverine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/431290/86ee05d60a3c3120e94f0c823c989ed5d6cebb07.jpg"},{"name":"Wheel A","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/431290/cb006c5bc67953b937576fd35b3ab0e4e6105f29.jpg"},{"name":"Solid Smack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/app